Description: # Python client for dnsdist console
        
        ![PyPI - Python Version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/dnsdist-console)
        ![](https://github.com/dmachard/dnsdist_console/workflows/Publish%20to%20PyPI/badge.svg)
